headline: Has DuPont’s Strong 2024 Rally Already Priced In Its Fair Value?
summary: If you are wondering whether DuPont de Nemours at around $41 a share is still a smart buy or if the easy gains are behind it, you are in the right place for a clear eyed look at value. The stock has climbed 0.8% over the last week and 8.9% over the past month, while still sitting on a steep 45.3% year to date move, yet it has delivered a solid 30.4% return over 1 year and 56.1% over 5 years.
